-a)+(f^('')(a))/(2!)(x-a)^2+(f^((3))(a))/(3!)(x-a)^3+...+(f^((n))(a))/(n!)(=
x-a)^n+....   " height=3D"42"></td><td align=3D"right" width=3D"3">
